            "title": "滬股半日跌近1%　創業板跌1.7%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深股市半日跌近1%或以上。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜合指數半日失守3400點，報3376點，跌31點，跌幅0.94%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成份指數報10725點，跌154點，跌幅1.42%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數報2162點，跌37點，跌幅1.7%。</p>\n</div>",
